<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. ضَجَّوْا وَصَاحُوا زَمَانًا لَيْسَ يَنْفَعُهُمْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>دُعَاءُ دَاعٍ وَلا تَسْلِيمُ مُصْطَبِرِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَكُلُّ يَوْمٍ لَهُمْ فِي طُولِ مُدَّتِهِمْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>نَزْعٌ شَدِيدٌ مِن التَّعْذِيبِ وَالسَّعَرِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>كَمْ بَيْنَ دَارِ هَوَانٍ لا انْقِضَاءَ لَهَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَدَارِ أَمْنٍ وَخُلْدٍ دَائِمِ الدَّهَرِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>دَارِ الَّذِينَ اتَّقُوْا مَوْلاهُمُ وَسَعَوْا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>قَصْدًا لِنَيْلِ رِضَاهُ سَعْيَ مُؤْتَمِرِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَآمِنُوا وَاسْتَقَامُوا مِثْلَ مَا أُمِرُوا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَاسْتَغْرَقُوا وَقْتَهُمْ فِي الصَّوْمِ وَالسَّهَرِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَجَاهَدُوا وَانْتَهَوْا عَمَّا يُبَاعِدُهُمْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>عَنْ بَابِهِ وَاسْتَلانُوا كُلَّ ذِي وَعَرِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>جَنَّاتُ عَدْنٍ لَهُمْ مَا يَشْتَهُونَ بِهَا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فِي مَقْعَدِ الصِّدْقِ بَيْنَ الرَّوْضِ وَالزَّهَرِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>بِنَاؤُهَا فِضَّةٌ قَدْ زَانَهَا ذَهَبٌ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَطِينُهَا الْمِسْكُ وَالْحَصْبَا مِنَ الدُّرَرِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>أَوْرَاقُهَا ذَهَبٌ مِنْهَا الْغُصُونُ دَنَتْ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>بِكُلِّ نُوعٍ مِن الرَّيْحَانِ وَالثَّمَرِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَوْرَاقُهَا حُلَلٌ شَفَافَةٌ خُلِقَتْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَاللُّؤْلؤُ الرَّطْبُ وَالْمُرْجَانُ فِي الشَّجَرِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>